        "text_mEJtMk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Cut with a performance fit and moderate compression designed for long rides without feeling overbuilt.</p><p>Over six years, these bibs have been shaped by steady testing and feedback from riders who spend long days in the saddle, which is probably why they’ve become the pair many people buy again and again. The straps sit flat and out of the way, and the leg grippers hold everything in place without squeezing.</p><p>The goal was simple: a droptail cargo bib short that just works, ride after ride.</p>",
