        },
        "text_ndMKEa": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>These bibs perform just like \"normal\" bibs with no pockets. The great thing about cargo bibs is the flexibility they provide. Flexibility to spread your items throughout more pockets, or to skip a regular jersey in favor of a trail shirt or pull-over. Ever fumble with your phone or wallet when getting coffee? Simply slide them into the left or right cargo pockets.</p><p>We admit we were cargo bib skeptics at first, especially since we are all about the bar bag. But after spending time with these, paired with a bar bag... we are sold. - Check out our <a href=\"https://www.ornotbike.com/pages/best-cargo-bib-shorts-2026\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The Best Cargo Bib Shorts in 2026\">Best Cargo Bib Shorts 2026 Guide</a>.</p>",
